{
  "texts": [
    "Spatial-temporal Transformer networks introduced a temporal Transformer block to capture the temporal dependencies and a spatial Transformer block to assist a graph convolution network to capture more spatial-spatial dependencies [98].",
    "3There are also applications for event prediction.",
    "Event forecasting or prediction aims to predict the times and marks of future events given the history of past events, which is often modeled by temporal point processes (TPP) [6].",
    "Self-attentive Hawkes process (SAHP) [7] and Transformer Hawkes process (THP) [8] adopt Transformer encoder architecture to summarize the influence of historical events and compute the intensity function for event prediction.",
    "They modify the positional encoding by translating time intervals into sinusoidal functions to utilize interval between events."
  ]
}